reviews.review: The movie was so disappointing. Similarly to the Force Awakens the plot was not original. It was predictable if you saw Return of the Jedi. The callbacks to the original were not subtle nor artistic. As a long time Star Wars fan this was a major let down. The final battle between Rey and Palpatine should have been a fight that topped all previous duels since this is supposed to be the last movie of the Skywalker saga. Instead it was emotionless and lacked any excitement. This final battle had none of the heart that Luke vs Darth Vader had. Overall this was the weakest movie of the last trilogy. They canâ€™t end the Skywalker story this way.
This was a great conclusion to the newest trilogy, will definitely come to see it again.
Loved it, fun not stop action and left the theater feeling happy. Took my wife, son (11) and parents and they all give it a thumbs up. It has become my son's favorite Star Wars movie.

i thought it was a great ending to a long story. the movie was action packed and entertaining through out. no spoilers here but there are surprises as well as bringing back many memories of the series through out the years

It was utterly a poot attempt to fix TFA's and TLJ's massive gaping plotholes and bad writing. I have to admit they really tried. But as Star Wars says "Do or Do not do , there is no try". It failed to give characters deph and motivation other than "Just be there". Daisy was confused and utterly low. The repurposed Leia scenes made no sense ans was weird. Palpatine's appearance was also contradictory and shallow. Simply if I could go back in time and get the money back...i would.NOT RECOMMENDED TO STAR WARS FANS!

Disney shits on 40 years of story telling by killing off every main character from the original saga. 
Up until the ending I was satisfied with the fan service and enjoyed much of the movie. Ultimately the ending enraged me after rewatching the 8 previous movies it seems like Disney would rather remake the Star Wars universe than use the original source material.
